You sure are a capitalist, Director Su.

533
00:38:29,939 --> 00:38:34,000
You won't let yourself suffer losses even when having a bowl of wonton.

534
00:38:34,000 --> 00:38:37,499
So aren't you going to reconsider what I just said?

535
00:38:37,499 --> 00:38:39,570
No.

536
00:38:39,570 --> 00:38:42,329
What a penny-pincher, you won't even lend me 500 yuan.

537
00:38:46,710 --> 00:38:48,800
This was what you were talking about?

538
00:38:48,800 --> 00:38:50,750
Why did you bring Qin Yinan up then?

539
00:38:50,750 --> 00:38:53,569
Well... This is his hometown.

540
00:38:53,569 --> 00:38:56,869
He used to tell me that the night market here is worth a visit.

541
00:38:58,630 --> 00:39:00,040
So?

